### Car Service API - HTTP Request Collection
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### Run in order: create data -> execute operations -> verify

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ============ CUSTOMERS CRUD ============

### Create customer 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Иван Петров",
  "email": "ivan@mail.ru",
  "phone": "+7-912-111-2233"
}

### Create customer 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Мария Сидорова",
  "email": "maria@mail.ru",
  "phone": "+7-912-222-3344"
}

### Get all customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers

### Get customer by id (use id from create response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1

### Update customer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Иван Петров (обновлён)",
  "email": "ivan.updated@mail.ru",
  "phone": "+7-912-111-2234"
}

### ============ MECHANICS CRUD ============

### Create mechanic 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mechanics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Сергей Мастеров",
  "specialization": "Двигатель"
}

### Create mechanic 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mechanics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ольга Слесарёва",
  "specialization": "Кузов"
}

### Get all mechanics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mechanics

### Get mechanic by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mechanics/1

### Update mechanic
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/mechanics/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Сергей Мастеров",
  "specialization": "Двигатель и трансмиссия"
}

